                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿یَـٰۤأَیُّهَا ٱلۡمُدَّثِّرُ ۝١﴾ النَّبِيّ صَلَّى اللَّه عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ وَأَصْله الْمُتَدَثِّر أُدْغِمَتْ التَّاء فِي الدَّال أَيْ الْمُتَلَفِّف بِثِيَابِهِ عِنْد نُزُول الْوَحْي عَلَيْهِ</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "74:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿قُمۡ فَأَنذِرۡ ۝٢﴾ خَوِّفْ أَهْل مَكَّة النَّار إنْ لَمْ يُؤْمِنُوا</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "74:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَرَبَّكَ فَكَبِّرۡ ۝٣﴾ عَظِّمْ عَنْ إشْرَاك الْمُشْرِكِينَ</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "74:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَثِیَابَكَ فَطَهِّرۡ ۝٤﴾ عَنْ النَّجَاسَة أَوْ قَصِّرْهَا خِلَاف جَرّ الْعَرَب ثِيَابهمْ خُيَلَاء فَرُبَّمَا أَصَابَتْهَا نَجَاسَة</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "74:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَٱلرُّجۡزَ﴾ فَسَّرَهُ النَّبِيّ صَلَّى اللَّه عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ بِالْأَوْثَانِ ﴿فَٱهۡجُرۡ ۝٥﴾ أَيْ دُمْ عَلَى هَجْره</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "74:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَلَا تَمۡنُن تَسۡتَكۡثِرُ ۝٦﴾ بِالرَّفْعِ حَال أَيْ لَا تُعْطِ شَيْئًا لِتَطْلُب أَكْثَر مِنْهُ وَهَذَا خَاصّ بِهِ صَلَّى اللَّه عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ لِأَنَّهُ مَأْمُور بِأَجْمَل الْأَخْلَاق وَأَشْرَف الْآدَاب</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "74:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَلِرَبِّكَ فَٱصۡبِرۡ ۝٧﴾ عَلَى الْأَوَامِر وَالنَّوَاهِي</h2>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "74:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَإِذَا نُقِرَ فِی ٱلنَّاقُورِ ۝٨﴾ نُفِخَ فِي الصُّور وَهُوَ الْقَرْن النَّفْخَة الثَّانِيَة</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "74:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَذَ ٰ⁠لِكَ﴾ أَيْ وَقْت النَّقْر ﴿یَوۡمَىِٕذࣲ﴾ بَدَل مِمَّا قَبْله الْمُبْتَدَأ وَبُنِيَ لِإِضَافَتِهِ إلَى غَيْر مُتَمَكِّن وَخَبَر الْمُبْتَدَأ ﴿یَوۡمٌ عَسِیرٌ ۝٩﴾ وَالْعَامِل فِي إذَا مَا دَلَّتْ عَلَيْهِ الْجُمْلَة اشْتَدَّ الْأَمْر</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "74:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿عَلَى ٱلۡكَـٰفِرِینَ غَیۡرُ یَسِیرࣲ ۝١٠﴾ فِيهِ دَلَالَة عَلَى أَنَّهُ يَسِير عَلَى الْمُؤْمِنِينَ فِي عُسْره</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "74:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ذَرۡنِی﴾ اُتْرُكْنِي ﴿وَمَنۡ خَلَقۡتُ﴾ عَطْف عَلَى الْمَفْعُول أَوْ مَفْعُول مَعَهُ ﴿وَحِیدࣰا ۝١١﴾ حَال مِنْ مَنْ أَوْ مِنْ ضَمِيره الْمَحْذُوف مِنْ خَلَقْت مُنْفَرِدًا بِلَا أَهْل وَلَا مَال هُوَ الْوَلِيد بْن المغيرة المخزومي</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "74:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَجَعَلۡتُ لَهُۥ مَالࣰا مَّمۡدُودࣰا ۝١٢﴾ وَاسِعًا مُتَّصِلًا مِنْ الزُّرُوع وَالضُّرُوع وَالتِّجَارَة</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "74:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَبَنِینَ﴾ عَشَرَة أَوْ أَكْثَر ﴿شُهُودࣰا ۝١٣﴾ يَشْهَدُونَ الْمَحَافِل وتسمع شهاداتهم</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "74:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَمَهَّدتُّ﴾ بَسَطْت ﴿لَهُۥ﴾ فِي الْعَيْش وَالْعُمُر وَالْوَلَد ﴿تَمۡهِیدࣰا ۝١٤﴾</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "74:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ثُمَّ یَطۡمَعُ أَنۡ أَزِیدَ ۝١٥﴾</h2>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "74:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿كَلَّاۤۖ﴾ لَا أَزِيدهُ عَلَى ذَلِكَ ﴿إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ لِـَٔایَـٰتِنَا﴾ الْقُرْآن ﴿عَنِیدࣰا ۝١٦﴾ مُعَانِدًا</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "74:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿سَأُرۡهِقُهُۥ﴾ أُكَلِّفهُ ﴿صَعُودًا ۝١٧﴾ مَشَقَّة مِنْ الْعَذَاب أَوْ جَبَلًا مِنْ نَار يَصْعَد فِيهِ ثُمَّ يَهْوِي أبدا</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "74:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿إِنَّهُۥ فَكَّرَ﴾ فِيمَا يَقُول فِي الْقُرْآن الَّذِي سَمِعَهُ مِنْ النَّبِيّ صَلَّى اللَّه عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ ﴿وَقَدَّرَ ۝١٨﴾ فِي نَفْسه ذَلِكَ</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "74:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَقُتِلَ﴾ لُعِنَ وَعُذِّبَ ﴿كَیۡفَ قَدَّرَ ۝١٩﴾ عَلَى أَيّ حال كان تقديره</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "74:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ثُمَّ قُتِلَ كَیۡفَ قَدَّرَ ۝٢٠﴾</h2>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "74:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ثُمَّ نَظَرَ ۝٢١﴾ فِي وُجُوه قَوْمه أَوْ فِيمَا يَقْدَح بِهِ فِيهِ</p>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "74:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ثُمَّ عَبَسَ﴾ قَبَضَ وَجْهه وَكَلَّحَهُ ضِيقًا بِمَا يَقُول ﴿وَبَسَرَ ۝٢٢﴾ زَادَ فِي الْقَبْض وَالْكُلُوح</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "74:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ﴾ عَنْ الْإِيمَان ﴿وَٱسۡتَكۡبَرَ ۝٢٣﴾ تَكَبَّرَ عَنْ اتِّبَاع النَّبِيّ صَلَّى اللَّه عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "74:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿فَقَالَ﴾ فِيمَا جَاءَ بِهِ ﴿إِنۡ﴾ مَا ﴿هَـٰذَاۤ إِلَّا سِحۡرࣱ یُؤۡثَرُ ۝٢٤﴾ يُنْقَل عَنْ السَّحَرَة</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "74:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿إِنۡ﴾ مَا ﴿هَـٰذَاۤ إِلَّا قَوۡلُ ٱلۡبَشَرِ ۝٢٥﴾ كَمَا قَالُوا إنَّمَا يُعَلِّمهُ بشر</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "74:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿سَأُصۡلِیهِ﴾ أُدْخِلهُ ﴿سَقَرَ ۝٢٦﴾ جَهَنَّم</h2>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "74:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَمَاۤ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا سَقَرُ ۝٢٧﴾ تعظيم لشأنها</h2>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "74:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿لَا تُبۡقِی وَلَا تَذَرُ ۝٢٨﴾ شَيْئًا مِنْ لَحْم وَلَا عَصَب إلَّا أَهْلَكَتْهُ ثُمَّ يَعُود كما كان</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "74:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 106,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_jalalayn",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Jalalayn",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لَوَّاحَةࣱ لِّلۡبَشَرِ ۝٢٩﴾ مُحَرِّقَة لِظَاهِرِ الْجِلْد</h2>"
        },
